Titolo: Metaltech: Battledrome

Anno: 1994

Descrizione: Metaltech: Battledrome is a mecha-style simulation video game in the Metaltech series developed by Dynamix and released in 1994. It was published alongside its companion game Earthsiege and shares roughly the same gaming mechanics and strategy although in a completely different setting.

Genere: Simulation

Valutazione: N/A
